1
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:26,890
♪Lights of swords are like
a splash of rivers♪

2
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:34,320
♪Shadows of swords cover the seasons♪

3
00:00:34,700 --> 00:00:38,090
♪The clear water cuts off the gorge♪

4
00:00:38,910 --> 00:00:42,190
♪Which is facing the armed army♪

5
00:00:42,410 --> 00:00:45,780
♪Missing a pot of cold wine♪

6
00:00:46,520 --> 00:00:49,590
♪Drunk in the middle of sand♪

7
00:00:49,670 --> 00:00:53,520
♪The place of peace of mind
is my hometown♪

8
00:00:54,280 --> 00:00:57,240
♪But my hometown is by your side♪

9
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,520
♪Who forgets about the grudges
in the past♪

10
00:01:01,830 --> 00:01:04,920
♪Don’t blame the west wind
for your tears♪

11
00:01:04,920 --> 00:01:08,700
♪To meet and to part are like a dream♪

12
00:01:09,430 --> 00:01:12,610
♪Well-armed with armor and weapons♪

13
00:01:12,610 --> 00:01:16,960
♪Where the surging river is going♪

14
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:22,960
♪Together we go to the end of the world♪

15
00:01:24,380 --> 00:01:29,980
=Legend of Fei=

16
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,940
=Episode 28=

17
00:01:34,230 --> 00:01:36,590
Will your master also go to
Demon-Extermination Assembly?

18
00:01:36,590 --> 00:01:37,590
Yes.

19
00:01:38,120 --> 00:01:40,000
They’re close friends.

20
00:01:41,440 --> 00:01:44,000
If your master is in danger,

21
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,910
he definitely won’t just stand by.

22
00:01:46,310 --> 00:01:47,120
Where is your master?

23
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,550
I’ll take you there now.

24
00:01:48,550 --> 00:01:51,270
Mr. Xie said that
you’re one of us.

25
00:01:52,510 --> 00:01:53,190
Jiachen.

26
00:01:53,190 --> 00:01:53,440
Yes.

27
00:01:53,440 --> 00:01:54,680
Go inside to report first.

28
00:01:55,080 --> 00:01:55,630
Yes.

29
00:01:58,230 --> 00:01:59,720
-This way, please.
-Okay.

30
00:02:03,910 --> 00:02:05,950
Xie Meimei. Xie Meimei.

31
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:07,720
Why didn’t you go to
the southern border?

32
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,550
Why must you come to Lingling Town?

33
00:03:21,910 --> 00:03:22,800
Miss Zhou.

34
00:03:23,110 --> 00:03:24,110
What’s wrong?

35
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:27,000
It’s nothing.

36
00:03:30,550 --> 00:03:31,240
Let’s go.

37
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:46,320
What are you looking at?

38
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:51,470
Thank you for saving my life.

39
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:54,320
I’m willing to be your servant
in my next life to repay your help.

40
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:57,320
Quit it, Qian Suiyou.

41
00:03:57,320 --> 00:04:00,320
Save those useless fancy words
you learned from books to yourself.

42
00:04:01,270 --> 00:04:03,440
Let me put it this way.

43
00:04:03,440 --> 00:04:04,720
Thank you so much.

44
00:04:05,440 --> 00:04:06,910
You saved me from my misery.

45
00:04:06,910 --> 00:04:08,110
What you did was like

46
00:04:08,440 --> 00:04:09,800
giving me a second life.

47
00:04:10,270 --> 00:04:12,030
That’s more like it.

48
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:13,830
Last time I saw you,

49
00:04:13,830 --> 00:04:15,630
you were so intimate with Miss Zhou.

50
00:04:15,630 --> 00:04:18,350
Being with her is miserable now?

51
00:04:20,270 --> 00:04:21,760
It’s always like this.

52
00:04:21,760 --> 00:04:24,480
When they meet new people,
the old ones become unimportant.

53
00:04:24,670 --> 00:04:27,350
Miss Lingyu,
haven’t you seen enough?

54
00:04:27,350 --> 00:04:30,320
What a pity!

55
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:32,790
For what?

56
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:35,510
How could a nice man like you

57
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:37,550
get abandoned?

58
00:04:39,510 --> 00:04:41,040
Not abandoned.

59
00:04:41,350 --> 00:04:43,270
Fei is a nice girl.

60
00:04:43,270 --> 00:04:45,640
I’m not worthy of her.

61
00:04:46,200 --> 00:04:47,070
Why do you always dress up

62
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:49,830
like Qian Suiyou?

63
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:54,160
Yuyi Troupe has many ladies.

64
00:04:54,160 --> 00:04:56,160
It’s inconvenient for
a young man like me

65
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,670
to come in and out.

66
00:04:57,670 --> 00:04:59,600
It’s better to stay away from troubles.

67
00:05:02,230 --> 00:05:03,440
And I have to say it again.

68
00:05:03,440 --> 00:05:04,950
Thank you so much.

69
00:05:04,950 --> 00:05:07,070
I’m willing to be your servant
in my next life to repay your help.

70
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,510
But today I have
important matters to attend to.

71
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:09,350
I have to say goodbye for now.

72
00:05:09,350 --> 00:05:11,480
See you again in the future.

73
00:05:16,040 --> 00:05:17,200
What?

74
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:19,000
What is he hiding from?

75
00:05:49,110 --> 00:05:50,070
Xie Meimei,

76
00:05:51,230 --> 00:05:54,230
deep in your heart,
you want her to come.

77
00:05:55,760 --> 00:05:57,510
But when you see her,
you turn around and flee.

78
00:05:58,270 --> 00:05:59,950
When she’s not after you, you...

79
00:06:01,550 --> 00:06:02,830
This is hilarious.

80
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,880
I’m fine. I’m fine.

81
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,480
Sir.

82
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,230
You’re quite tough.

83
00:06:17,230 --> 00:06:18,390
You don’t get hurt easily.

84
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,550
I’m fine.

85
00:06:25,070 --> 00:06:26,880
Why did you get into the carriage?

86
00:06:27,550 --> 00:06:29,110
Young girl.

87
00:06:29,110 --> 00:06:31,440
You’re very impolite to the elders.

88
00:06:31,440 --> 00:06:32,440
Excuse me.

89
00:06:40,670 --> 00:06:42,070
Why are you afraid to look at me?

90
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:49,200
Why don’t you keep running?

91
00:06:50,230 --> 00:06:53,160
How am I supposed to run
when you’re holding me?

92
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:54,550
So you indeed want to flee?

93
00:06:54,550 --> 00:06:55,830
You sent those

94
00:06:56,390 --> 00:06:57,720
Route Gang members?

95
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:58,390
Yes.

96
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,350
But it’s not easy to catch you.

97
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:02,790
It took Route Gang so long

98
00:07:02,790 --> 00:07:04,480
before they could find you.

99
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,950
That’s pretty bad for their reputation.

100
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:07,950
But I’ve thought it through.

101
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:10,110
If this doesn’t work out,
I’ll go to Huo Liantao’s assembly

102
00:07:10,110 --> 00:07:11,640
to find you.

103
00:07:12,270 --> 00:07:13,110
How do you like that?

104
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,270
Did you know it was me the moment

105
00:07:18,270 --> 00:07:19,390
I got in the carriage?

106
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:24,110
So you followed me all the way here.

107
00:07:27,320 --> 00:07:28,230
Fei.

108
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:31,070
That broke the rules.

109
00:07:31,550 --> 00:07:32,270
How about this?

110
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:34,920
Let’s do this again?

111
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:51,160
I haven’t seen you for days.

112
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:52,760
Why are you trying to fight me
the moment we meet?

113
00:08:14,650 --> 00:08:15,880
Amazing.

114
00:08:15,880 --> 00:08:17,550
You are playing Goose-breaking Blades
crazily.

115
00:08:20,000 --> 00:08:21,440
Are you really this mad?

116
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,470
Fei.

117
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,550
How’s your injury?

118
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,520
You told me when you were
at Fortress of the Forty-Eight

119
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,030
that Bone-chilling is

120
00:08:57,030 --> 00:08:58,080
the deadliest poison in the world.

121
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:06,150
Those who are poisoned

122
00:09:06,150 --> 00:09:08,080
will start to chill from their bones.

123
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,440
When they die,

124
00:09:10,080 --> 00:09:11,670
their whole body will be frozen.

125
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,840
How do you know that?

126
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:20,150
I’ve been traveling around the world.

127
00:09:20,150 --> 00:09:21,320
Well...

128
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,760
Cut it out.

129
00:09:24,590 --> 00:09:26,030
I won’t believe you anyway.

130
00:09:27,590 --> 00:09:31,030
Maybe it’s because I’m knowledgeable.

131
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:33,670
I know all about
the world and its history.

132
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:38,440
The other day, I asked you
where you learned your martial art.

133
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:40,110
You hit my lethargy point.

134
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:41,280
You put me to sleep.

135
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:43,910
Why?

136
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:47,200
You were injured.

137
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,150
Fei.

138
00:09:48,150 --> 00:09:50,000
You need to rest when you’re injured.

139
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:52,440
Why can’t you just let go of
those trivial questions?

140
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:54,520
You are always asking about
this and that.

141
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,350
No one can put up with that.

142
00:09:56,350 --> 00:09:58,000
I had to put you to sleep.

143
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:12,550
Fortress of the Forty-Eight
is still recovering from the incident.

144
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,710
Why do you have time to

145
00:10:18,640 --> 00:10:20,760
have fun at Lingling Town?

146
00:10:26,150 --> 00:10:27,640
I haven’t seen my mom for a while.

147
00:10:30,230 --> 00:10:32,200
I just met her briefly.

148
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,440
Then I sneaked out of the mountain.

149
00:10:34,230 --> 00:10:36,200
I followed the ambiguous information

150
00:10:36,200 --> 00:10:38,000
Route Gang has given me.

151
00:10:39,350 --> 00:10:40,400
I pursued.

152
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:44,590
I searched.

153
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:52,000
How dare you say that

154
00:10:52,000 --> 00:10:54,110
I’m here to have fun?

155
00:10:56,400 --> 00:10:58,470
She came for me?

156
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,960
Of course, I came because of
the ripple-shaped object

157
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,350
on Huo Liantao’s invitation.

158
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:11,790
What do you think
I am here for?

159
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:22,000
No one was talking about the Color of
Ocean and Heaven a few months back.

160
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:23,280
But now so many forces

161
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:26,790
are after it.

162
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:29,880
Huo Liantao’s invitation is determined

163
00:11:29,880 --> 00:11:32,910
to make every household
know about this.

164
00:11:33,550 --> 00:11:34,440
Even the Demons know that

165
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:36,550
Fortress of the Forty-Eight
has two important objects.

166
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:37,880
If I don’t try to figure it out myself,

167
00:11:39,280 --> 00:11:40,520
I will get dragged into

168
00:11:40,520 --> 00:11:41,790
this mess anyway, won’t I?

169
00:11:43,550 --> 00:11:45,440
Are you satisfied with this answer?

170
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,030
Fei.

171
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,640
I...

172
00:11:59,230 --> 00:12:00,230
Tortoise Master comes!

173
00:12:01,340 --> 00:12:02,440
Run!

174
00:12:24,700 --> 00:12:28,180
(Ding Kui, Tortoise Master
of Four-guardian Mountain)

175
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:33,030
I already have one foot in the grave.

176
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:34,790
Why do I have to drag her down?

177
00:12:36,710 --> 00:12:37,760
What?

178
00:12:41,960 --> 00:12:43,200
Say it.

179
00:12:47,470 --> 00:12:48,790
Look that way.

180
00:12:57,030 --> 00:12:59,230
Tortoise Master
of the Four-guardian Mountain

181
00:12:59,230 --> 00:13:01,230
made such a big entrance in town.

182
00:13:01,230 --> 00:13:03,520
It seems that he’s here
to stir up trouble.

183
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,550
You know who Tortoise Master
of the Four-guardian Mountain is,

184
00:13:07,550 --> 00:13:09,470
don’t you?

185
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:11,590
I know.

186
00:13:11,590 --> 00:13:13,000
Of course, I do.

187
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:16,030
I not only know him,
but I’ve also beaten up

188
00:13:16,280 --> 00:13:17,400
some of his pawns.

189
00:13:19,790 --> 00:13:21,200
You!

190
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:23,110
You don’t always get into trouble.

191
00:13:23,110 --> 00:13:24,150
But once you do,

192
00:13:24,150 --> 00:13:25,670
you mess around with
those who’re big and mighty.

193
00:13:25,670 --> 00:13:27,000
So what?

194
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,760
Just some of his pawns.

195
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:29,470
Do I have to make a report

196
00:13:29,470 --> 00:13:31,000
in advance for beating them?

197
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,320
You!

198
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:35,590
You are...

199
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:46,200
You sneak attacked me in
Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

200
00:13:46,350 --> 00:13:48,080
Now I sneak attacked you.

201
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:49,710
We’re even now.

202
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,960
What’s the use of these long legs?
Might as well cut them.

203
00:14:08,180 --> 00:14:12,670
(Lingling Town)

204
00:14:12,670 --> 00:14:13,520
Look.

205
00:14:13,760 --> 00:14:15,080
This is Lingling Town.

206
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,030
Why did Ding Kui

207
00:14:38,030 --> 00:14:40,520
rob my invitation?

208
00:14:42,390 --> 00:14:44,560
The four masters of
Four-guardian Mountain.

209
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:47,030
Dragon Master, Zheng Luosheng,
is deceitful.

210
00:14:47,030 --> 00:14:50,590
Phoenix Master, Mu Xiaoqiao,
is eccentric.

211
00:14:50,590 --> 00:14:54,200
White Tiger Master, Feng Feihua,
can’t distinguish right or wrong.

212
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,640
Tortoise Master, Ding Kui,
is capricious.

213
00:14:56,910 --> 00:14:59,200
Our Xingnan Sect is small and weak.

214
00:14:59,200 --> 00:15:01,200
Of course, they’re going to pick on us.

215
00:15:01,200 --> 00:15:02,910
He wants to find an invitation

216
00:15:02,910 --> 00:15:04,950
and rightfully walks into
Demon-Extermination Assembly.

217
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,640
But I didn’t expect them

218
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:08,950
to make such a scene.

219
00:15:08,950 --> 00:15:11,000
It seems that things are going to change

220
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,320
in Lingling Town.

221
00:15:23,640 --> 00:15:24,910
Is that Zhou Fei?

222
00:15:25,710 --> 00:15:26,950
That seems to be her.

223
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,350
What is she pushing?

224
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:37,800
Miss Zhou.

225
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:39,800
I picked up an old opera writer.

226
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:40,680
Zhou Fei.

227
00:15:40,680 --> 00:15:41,560
Fei.

228
00:15:41,560 --> 00:15:43,080
Where have you been?

229
00:15:43,560 --> 00:15:44,880
Chuchu.

230
00:15:44,880 --> 00:15:46,510
You came right on time.
Come help me.

231
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:47,510
Let me help you.

232
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:48,390
No need.

233
00:15:49,910 --> 00:15:51,240
My cousin said no.

234
00:15:55,880 --> 00:15:57,150
Well.

235
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:02,120
Sir.

236
00:16:02,320 --> 00:16:03,680
Can we have one room, please?

237
00:16:06,440 --> 00:16:08,440
Why is this old man so heavy?

238
00:16:28,390 --> 00:16:30,440
Isn’t this Mr. Xie?

239
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:31,440
What’s going on?

240
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,390
What’s wrong with his face?

241
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,030
That’s a long story.

242
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,270
Fei.

243
00:16:40,950 --> 00:16:42,350
Have you disabled him?

244
00:16:42,350 --> 00:16:43,470
Li Yan.

245
00:16:44,120 --> 00:16:44,950
Stay there.

246
00:16:45,390 --> 00:16:46,200
Come back.

247
00:16:49,950 --> 00:16:51,440
Why are you here?

248
00:16:51,680 --> 00:16:52,560
No.

249
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:54,150
How did you escape?

250
00:16:54,150 --> 00:16:54,510
I...

251
00:16:54,510 --> 00:16:55,640
I don’t want to listen to your excuses.

252
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:56,680
You must find the secret service

253
00:16:56,680 --> 00:16:58,000
and go back home immediately.

254
00:16:58,000 --> 00:17:00,240
Go back to
Fortress of the Forty-Eight right now.

255
00:17:01,470 --> 00:17:03,320
You’re her brother.

256
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:05,440
Can’t you be nicer to your own sister?

257
00:17:05,440 --> 00:17:07,480
People from Fortress of the Forty-Eight

258
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:09,360
are all so mean.

259
00:17:09,360 --> 00:17:11,800
Can’t you be gentler
to your own sisters?

260
00:17:12,840 --> 00:17:16,320
Li Yan, you’re tough now.

261
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:19,200
You even have the full support of
those you’ve cheated.

262
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:20,990
-That’s enough.
-Bonehead.

263
00:17:20,990 --> 00:17:22,030
In all these years of my life,

264
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:24,320
this is the first time
someone stood up for me.

265
00:17:25,990 --> 00:17:27,030
Sheng.

266
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:30,230
I heard that Yuyi Troupe is
in Lingling Town.

267
00:17:30,230 --> 00:17:31,150
Can you invite Madam Nichang

268
00:17:31,150 --> 00:17:32,910
for me?

269
00:17:34,680 --> 00:17:36,440
Sure. No problem.

270
00:17:46,480 --> 00:17:48,320
What are you doing?

271
00:17:48,800 --> 00:17:49,870
Go ahead.

272
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:18,460
(Huo’s Manor)

273
00:18:27,030 --> 00:18:28,680
Our master said that

274
00:18:29,270 --> 00:18:30,230
he won’t see any visitors today.

275
00:18:30,230 --> 00:18:32,320
