it’s impossible for Qian Suiyou
to break free.

545
00:39:22,560 --> 00:39:24,030
Even if Li Zheng is
locked on one side

546
00:39:24,030 --> 00:39:25,840
and Yin Wenlan is
locked on the other side,

547
00:39:25,840 --> 00:39:27,750
without knowing the right method,

548
00:39:27,750 --> 00:39:29,920
they’re never gonna
break free from this.

549
00:39:30,600 --> 00:39:31,920
Thank you, Madam.

550
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:32,950
You’re welcome.

551
00:39:34,750 --> 00:39:36,400
What on earth is this thing

552
00:39:36,400 --> 00:39:38,360
Madam Nichang gave you?

553
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,160
What are you doing?

554
00:40:19,230 --> 00:40:21,230
I’ll buy you a new one someday.

555
00:40:21,230 --> 00:40:22,320
No, no, no!

556
00:40:23,510 --> 00:40:25,160
How dare I?

557
00:40:25,160 --> 00:40:27,670
I should be grateful

558
00:40:27,670 --> 00:40:29,430
you didn’t draw the tortoise
on my face.

559
00:40:31,360 --> 00:40:33,190
You don’t have other good qualities.

560
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:34,710
But, at least,
you know when to behave yourself.

561
00:40:37,880 --> 00:40:40,320
Beauty... This...

562
00:40:45,600 --> 00:40:46,840
Well.

563
00:40:47,270 --> 00:40:49,230
How did you come up with

564
00:40:49,230 --> 00:40:51,030
this new position?

565
00:40:51,750 --> 00:40:54,470
At least, I’m a handsome guy.

566
00:40:54,470 --> 00:40:56,560
When I go out like this,

567
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:59,190
I have to either
bend down or lift my leg.

568
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:01,230
When I use the bathroom,
I have to stand on one foot.

569
00:41:03,710 --> 00:41:04,920
Well...

570
00:41:07,120 --> 00:41:08,160
I mean...

571
00:41:08,710 --> 00:41:09,600
Look at this.

572
00:41:10,080 --> 00:41:11,560
I’m standing like
I’m kicking a shuttlecock.

573
00:41:11,560 --> 00:41:13,270
Isn’t this hideous to look at?

574
00:41:14,990 --> 00:41:16,750
Blame Li Sheng for this.

575
00:41:23,160 --> 00:41:24,670
Don’t tell anyone else.

576
00:41:25,950 --> 00:41:26,950
Where should I chain him to?

577
00:41:31,230 --> 00:41:33,160
Not to this bed, of course.

578
00:41:33,160 --> 00:41:35,800
This bed can’t keep him chained.

579
00:41:35,800 --> 00:41:37,400
How about locking him with you?

580
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,600
No.

581
00:41:38,600 --> 00:41:40,320
He’s a man and you’re a woman.

582
00:41:41,670 --> 00:41:42,990
It’s not convenient.

583
00:41:46,710 --> 00:41:48,230
It’s indeed inconvenient.

584
00:42:02,750 --> 00:42:03,840
Put the lock on his foot.

585
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:09,840
That one.

586
00:42:33,670 --> 00:42:34,750
Perfect.

587
00:42:37,360 --> 00:42:38,640
He escaped my notice for a moment.

588
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,470
And he just put
the other end of the lock

589
00:42:40,470 --> 00:42:41,800
on your wrist.

590
00:42:41,800 --> 00:42:45,160
Otherwise,
I would’ve put it on your neck.

591
00:42:45,160 --> 00:42:46,470
Then you don’t have to stand like this.

592
00:42:46,470 --> 00:42:47,640
You can stand with your feet
in your mouth.

593
00:42:51,710 --> 00:42:52,640
Fine.

594
00:42:53,270 --> 00:42:54,670
You’ve grown up.

595
00:42:57,990 --> 00:43:00,990
As your master, I feel relieved.

596
00:43:02,880 --> 00:43:05,270
I’m hungry.
Is there anything I can eat?

597
00:43:06,230 --> 00:43:08,190
I spent a whole day
in the chase with you.

598
00:43:08,710 --> 00:43:10,560
I haven’t had any water or food.

599
00:43:11,600 --> 00:43:14,160
Sure. I’ll get you something to eat.

600
00:43:49,080 --> 00:43:50,160
Sir.

601
00:43:50,160 --> 00:43:51,800
From now on, the dishes for Mr. Xie

602
00:43:51,800 --> 00:43:53,510
must be as light as possible.

603
00:43:53,510 --> 00:43:54,510
And the food must be cold,

604
00:43:54,510 --> 00:43:55,840
not even warm.

605
00:43:56,800 --> 00:43:59,190
Miss, the weather is hot.

606
00:43:59,190 --> 00:44:00,670
But when the dishes are cold,

607
00:44:00,670 --> 00:44:03,230
the taste will be bad.

608
00:44:03,230 --> 00:44:04,640
Just do as I say.

609
00:44:05,800 --> 00:44:06,710
Thank you.

610
00:44:08,640 --> 00:44:10,230
It’s better than losing your life
for this.

611
00:44:11,670 --> 00:44:14,710
Miss.
There’s a Mr. Yang in the backyard.

612
00:44:14,710 --> 00:44:15,920
He’s been waiting for you for a while.

613
00:44:17,840 --> 00:44:19,360
Yang Jin?

614
00:44:46,670 --> 00:44:47,840
A contest is a contest.

615
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:49,400
Why are you cheating again?

616
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:50,640
Is this cheating?

617
00:44:50,640 --> 00:44:51,320
Come on.

618
00:44:51,430 --> 00:44:52,400
Wait! Wait! Wait!

619
00:44:54,120 --> 00:44:55,230
What?

620
00:44:55,750 --> 00:44:56,750
Are you scared?

621
00:44:58,030 --> 00:44:59,840
When Yang Jin

622
00:44:59,840 --> 00:45:01,320
hears the word blade,

623
00:45:01,320 --> 00:45:03,800
he’ll get so excited.

624
00:45:03,800 --> 00:45:04,840
He will become

625
00:45:04,840 --> 00:45:06,120
very gullible.

626
00:45:06,120 --> 00:45:07,160
To get rid of him,

627
00:45:07,160 --> 00:45:08,670
I need to trick him.

628
00:45:09,600 --> 00:45:11,270
Do you know why I come to town?

629
00:45:11,270 --> 00:45:12,670
To joust.

630
00:45:14,080 --> 00:45:15,080
No.

631
00:45:15,750 --> 00:45:17,510
I came here for
the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

632
00:45:17,510 --> 00:45:18,600
What color?

633
00:45:19,320 --> 00:45:21,120
The Color of Ocean and Heaven.

634
00:45:21,120 --> 00:45:22,640
It’s a legacy.

635
00:45:22,640 --> 00:45:25,640
It has collected the legacies
of the sects

636
00:45:25,640 --> 00:45:27,360
that have fallen because of
natural or man-made disasters.

637
00:45:27,360 --> 00:45:28,710
And…

638
00:45:28,990 --> 00:45:31,190
Have you heard of Reborn Pill?

639
00:45:31,190 --> 00:45:33,080
It can boost people’s force.

640
00:45:33,080 --> 00:45:34,190
Really?

641
00:45:34,470 --> 00:45:35,950
Of course, it’s true.

642
00:45:42,490 --> 00:45:46,000
♪Stars flow like river♪

643
00:45:47,060 --> 00:45:50,660
♪My yearning falls into the river♪

644
00:45:51,230 --> 00:45:55,300
♪Now that you’re in my life♪

645
00:45:55,550 --> 00:45:59,190
♪I will never be alone♪

646
00:45:59,190 --> 00:46:03,310
♪I haven’t seen the mountains with you♪

647
00:46:03,730 --> 00:46:08,160
♪Nor have I tied up your hair♪

648
00:46:08,820 --> 00:46:13,380
♪We haven’t finished our story in chaos♪

649
00:46:13,610 --> 00:46:18,240
♪The blade hasn’t been returned♪

650
00:46:18,430 --> 00:46:22,260
♪I fear not to roam the world with you♪

651
00:46:22,480 --> 00:46:27,170
♪When I go across the world for you♪

652
00:46:27,430 --> 00:46:31,170
♪I’m willing to shed blood for you♪

653
00:46:31,500 --> 00:46:36,590
♪Don’t mind whose land it is♪

654
00:46:36,590 --> 00:46:40,530
♪Where is home to the snowflake♪

655
00:46:40,530 --> 00:46:45,060
♪Come and melt in my embrace♪

656
00:46:45,680 --> 00:46:52,780
♪The spring sun is an invisible armor
that’ll hold♪

657
00:46:53,520 --> 00:46:58,150
♪The purest love is unadorned♪
